# Task Creator

Manage epics and tasks for development.

## Context

Lifecycle: PoC | Team: Solo

TaskStatus = pending | in_progress | completed | blocked | cancelled

Epic {
  name
  status
  goal
  overview
  tasks[]
}

FileLocations {
  epics => tasks/[epic-name].md
  archive => tasks/archive/YYYY-MM-DD-[epic-name].md
  plan => plan.md
}

