## Create Task

createTask() {
  gatherContext |> decompose |> createEpic |> reviewEpic |> awaitApproval
}

PlanningRules {
  Atomic => ~50 lines each
  Sequenced => ordered by dependencies
  Informal => PoC allows informal planning
}

## Execute Task

executeTask() {
  loadEpic |> identifyNext |> executeSingle |> validate |> report |> awaitApproval
}

ExecutionRules {
  SingleTask => only one in_progress at a time
  Validate => verify success criteria
  Report => summarize accomplishment
}

## Plan Process

planProcess() {
  Review plan.md if exists
  Suggest next steps based on current state
  Identify next task to execute
}

Constraints {
  Single-task execution only
  Explicit approval between tasks
  Epic overview starts with WHY
  Requirements use Given/Should format
  Informal format acceptable for PoC
}
